text: Austin Harris Mahone (born April 4, 1996) is an American pop singer- songwriter. He is signed to Young Money Entertainment. == Biography == Austin Mahone was born on 4 April 1996 in the United States. His career began in 2010, when he was 14. He released the single "Mmh Yeah" in January 2014 featuring Pitbull. == Discography == === As lead artist === ==== 2014 ==== * "Mmh Yeah" (featuring Pitbull) ==Gallery== File:Austin-Mahone B96 Summerbash 2012-06-16 (cropped).jpg|Mahone in 2012.
